WEBVTT

00:02:28.480 --> 00:02:32.766
But you tell me why should there be 
any violence in educational institutes?

00:02:34.160 --> 00:02:37.376
But I’ll admit one thing,

00:02:37.376 --> 00:02:41.080
When I went for Vipaasana,
I was in no such hurry for meditation.

00:02:41.080 --> 00:02:43.560
I mind wasn’t all that philosophical.


00:02:43.560 --> 00:02:46.560
My world had been shaken.

00:02:46.560 --> 00:02:50.736
I was scared about not
having friends anymore.

00:02:50.760 --> 00:02:54.136
Would anyone come and talk to me or not?

00:02:54.160 --> 00:02:56.930
The atmosphere was such that
I was worried

00:02:56.980 --> 00:02:59.330
if I would be able to
even complete my education.